title: CDMPHO Puri Recruitment 2025 - Walk-in-Interview for 22 Medical Officer , Dental Technician and Other Posts
description: Chief District Medical & Public Health Office, Puri (CDMPHO Puri) has declared the latest job notification for 202. To fill up the vacancies for 22 Medical Officers, Physiotherapists, Dental Technicians, Counsellors, and Accountants. Those candidates who have qualified in the BAMS, BUMS, BDS, MD/ MS, or Any Degree can grab this chance and apply for the CDMPHO Puri Recruitment 2025 . Here we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how...
